{
  "chapter": 220,
  "chapter_summary": "本章以国兴之死拉开序幕。管中邪当着项少龙面射杀国兴，嫁祸武士行馆刺杀储君案，矛头直指嫪毐。项少龙进宫与小盘、李斯、王龁等人商议对策。小盘欲藉机除嫪毐，项少龙力主留嫪制吕，避免吕不韦趁势坐大。李斯分析若杀嫪毐，太后朱姬威信尽失，吕不韦或可借朝臣之力成辅政大臣。项少龙又献策令成蟜领兵出征赵国，以暴露其与赵人勾结之实。随后项少龙率禁卫赴甘泉宫解围，驱散管中邪都卫，护送嫪毐与朱姬入宫。朱姬对储君怨怼甚深，经项少龙劝说方勉强赴宴。嫪毐对项少龙心存感激，却因朱姬召项少龙同车而暗生妒忌，暴露其心胸狭窄之本性。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来人停马！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xing",
      "speaker_name": "国兴",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大将军救我。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项统领见到了，国兴畏罪潜逃，下属不得不执行王令，把他射杀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "管中邪你竟敢当着本人眼前，射杀我都骑副统领？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项统领请勿误会，且听我详细道来，卑职奉有储君之令，追缉今早蓄意刺杀储君的凶徒，竟发觉凶徒由武士行馆馆主邱日升勾结前来咸阳。现在邱日升和凶徒全体落网，由仲父亲自审问，只有国兴拒捕逃走，项统领清楚看到，若认为卑职有失职之处，大可在储君、仲父和太后驾前提出来说好了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "给我搬尸！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "不准动他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项统领有命，卑职怎敢不依，我们走！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们终是低估了吕不韦，这一着确是毒辣之极，不但歼灭武士行馆，同时落了我们和嫪毐的面子；还可把矛头直接指向嫪毐，甚或杜璧和蒲鶮。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "吕不韦说不定还会趁机藉此事闹大，对付嫪毐和他的手下。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "他绝对动不了嫪毐，小俊你着人为国兴办理身后事，同时保护他的家人，我立即进宫面见储君，看看该如何应付此事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "储君正要找少龙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "咸阳城今晚定是插翼难飞之局，赵大和单美美……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我晓得了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "太傅免礼。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "眼前情况如何？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_he",
      "speaker_name": "王龁",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "管中邪刚才对武士行馆发动突袭，常杰和安金良当场被杀，邱日升给他们用棍把右手骨敲碎，行馆的二百多名核心武士全被擒拿，另外还审讯了两名受伤的刺客，证据确凿，使邱日升没得抵赖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那些人被送到我那里去，包括邱日升在内，都一口咬定是嫪毐指使的。由于渭南武士行馆之所以能够重开，全赖嫪毐大力保荐，所以嫪毐这次很难置身事外。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我找太傅，是要大家商量一下，是否正好藉此事除去嫪毐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嫪毐现在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他和大批心腹家将躲进甘泉宫去，太后曾两次派人来召储君，均给储君婉拒了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里没有半个人会为嫪毐之死叹一口气，但我们却不能不思量接踵而来的后果。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若此刻除去嫪毐，最受打击的当然是太后，这事若发生，太后将威信荡然，再难亲政主事，在那种情况下，只要吕不韦联结朝中大臣，说不定可真的成为辅政大臣，那我们凭黑龙辛苦弄出来的形势，将尽付东流。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_he",
      "speaker_name": "王龁",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们大可推举少龙以太傅身份辅政，尤其少龙今早护驾有功，兼之有黑龙出世，王绾和蔡泽等该知谁是真主，吕不韦要扭转形势，恐也扭转不来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_ping_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌平君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "没有人比少龙更适合做辅政大臣了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "储君和诸位这么看得起我，我自然很高兴，不过吕不韦今趟蓦然向嫪毐发难，固是怕我们革除管中邪之职，但亦未必真把矛头直指太后，可见定是另藏祸心，最后目的仍是要对抗我们那条黑龙。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "连我们都晓得邱日升和杜璧、蒲鶮暗中勾结，吕不韦没有理由不知道，但今趟他只针对嫪毐，一句不提杜璧和蒲鶮，其中确有点问题。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "会否是吕不韦已与杜璧和蒲鶮达成秘密协议，牺牲邱日升以扳倒嫪毐和太后，那只要再……嘿！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "昌文君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "廷尉大人的话绝非没有依据，因为蒲鶮由祭场返回来时，被吕不韦邀上他的车同坐，说不定他们在车内达成协议。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "寡人倒没有思及此点。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "王陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自黑龙出世，吕不韦和杜璧等都慌了手脚，在力图扳回大势下，这样做毫不稀奇。为今的问题在于我们对嫪毐看不顺眼，是否该趁机放倒他而已。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嫪毐算什么东西？眼前我们最大的敌人是吕不韦，故暂时最聪明的做法，仍是留嫪毐以制吕不韦，然后再设法清除成蟜等人，那时就毋须愁吕不韦还有什么作为了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们有什么方法对付成蟜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "那还不简单，着他领兵出征赵国，他和赵人的关系就无所遁形了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有比这更简单直接的方法了，但却须等待时机，现在黑龙才出世未久，寡人仍须一段时间去巩固权位。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_si",
      "speaker_name": "李斯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，我们该让嫪毐清楚知道吕不韦要毁了他，那他和吕不韦更势成水火。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "王陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事有利有弊，可以想见太后会由这次事件而清楚嫪毐的力量太过单薄，且会在以后不顾一切为他争取更大的权力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_he",
      "speaker_name": "王龁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论她如何力争，总轮不到他去当大将军，可以有多大作为？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "寡人立即去主持春宴，项太傅可带一队禁卫，把太后和那假阉宦护送来宫参与春宴，今天算他气数未尽好了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "谁敢阻我项少龙！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项统领不是去了参加春宴吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "text": "假若项某向管大人掷出飞针，不知管大人有多少成把握可以避过？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位最好不要妄动，我项少龙更非说笑，你们这样把甘泉宫团团包围，已犯下冒犯太后的大罪，我若要把你们处决，谁敢说我做得不对。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_shang",
      "speaker_name": "许商",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大将军误会了，我们只是奉仲父之命来保护太后吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xu_shang",
      "text": "原来如此，那你们给我立即撤走，保护之责，由此刻交给本大将军好了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谨遵大将军之命。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "嫪大人请放下吊桥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "嫪大人请恕少龙来迟之罪，太后是否受惊了？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "我知道邱日升的事后，立即进宫见驾，力陈邱日升勾通外人行刺储君之事绝对与嫪大人无关，储君方知错怪大人，命我立即来接太后和嫪大人入宫参与春宴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙真够朋友，我嫪毐必不会忘记，唉！我真不明白邱日升为何竟会做出如此蠢事来，对他有什么好处呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "对他当然大有好处，对杜璧和蒲鶮更是大大有好处，只是嫪兄就半分好处都没有了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这天杀的狗种，被人捉了还想陷害我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那忤逆子还记得我吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "太后……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "不用你插嘴！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "太后误会储君，他是刚知此事，故派出微臣和禁卫到来迎驾。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙你身为都骑统领，见到有人斗胆包围哀家的甘泉宫，竟不把这些人当场拿着，还有脸来见哀家？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "太后也不是第一天认识吕不韦吧？太后若怪责储君和我项少龙，岂非亲者痛、仇者快？若太后连嫪大人和小臣都不信任，还可相信什么人？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "是的！少龙确是微臣肝胆相照的朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是的！哀家可以信赖的人愈来愈少，不过哀家再没有赴宴的心情，你和嫪奉常去吧！但我却要你立誓保证奉常的安全。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "少龙敢以项上人头担保储君已明白邱日升一事与嫪大人绝无关系，但少龙仍要恳请太后入宫赴宴，否则徒教卑鄙小人暗中得意，以为成功损害太后和储君间的和谐关系。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "和谐关系？唉！不过哀家也好应和王儿详谈一下。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "请太后起驾！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙你陪我坐车，哀家有些话要问你。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 220,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    }
  ],
